            <div class="text-center">
                <a href="#lets-get-started" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500 transition-all shadow-md">
                    Get Started Now
